data.description: Welcome HOME to this Great 4-level home! Enjoy both formal and informal living spaces enhanced with vaulted ceilings, Three generous-sized upper level bedrooms offer comfort and privacy,  the primary retreat is on the lower level & boasts  a convenient en-suite bath. More living space found in the fully finished basement with newer easy-maintenance laminate floors and an additional bedroom that could also be perfect for an office, studio space or 2nd Primary Bedroom!!  Fully fenced-in backyard, Great location and conveniently located near community parks, minutes to shops, groceries, and restaurants makes this home a must see!!
